+## Deployment
+
+### Preview / Stage
+
+Push the `main` branch to trigger a netlify branch deploy. Your project will be available
+at https://main--project-name.netlify.app
+
+### Production
+
+Run the following command: `npx github:gridonic/dastro deploy`
+
+This will bump the project version in `package.json`, merge `main` into `production` and push it, which will
+a production deployment on netlify.
+
 ## Upgrading
 To upgrade to the latest version of Dastro, simply start the upgrade wizard and follow the steps as prompted.

